<html>
  <body>
    <p><%= @user.coach.first_name %>,</p>

    <p>Welcome to biblequizstats.net.  You have been added to our system as  
      a coach for <%= @user.coach.organization.name %>.
    </p>

    <p>To login into your account and set a password for this account, click the 
      URL below:
    </p>

    <p><a href='<%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token, host: @request) %>'><%= edit_password_reset_url(@user.password_reset_token, host: @request) %><a></p>

    <p>This link will take you to a page to set a new password. Please do this in 
      a timely fashion as the link will expire one week after receiving this email.  
      Once you set the password, you will be automatically logged into the system. 
      You can use this password for all future login attempts.  If you ever forget 
      this password (or wait too long to click the link), you can simply ask for 
      the password to be reset using the reset link on the site.
    </p>

    <p>If you have any questions or issues using this system, please contact the 
      <%= @setting.area_name %> administrator, <%= @setting.admin_name %>, at 
      <%= mail_to @setting.admin_email %> for assistance.  Thanks and best wishes.
    </p>

    <p>Sincerely,</p>

    <p>
      <%= @setting.admin_name %>
      <br />
      <%= @setting.area_name %> administrator
      <br />
      <a href="http://biblequizstats.net">http://biblequizstats.net</a>
    </p>

  </body>
</html>